{"tid":1510030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涂謹申：《緊急法》等同宣布戒嚴     反效果大　做法欠政治魄力","createTime":"2019-08-27T04:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T05:21:32.000Z","uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5cee6584eb12728b9b105551b95e0896708cd7e1","tid":1510030,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"涂謹申：《緊急法》反效果大　做法欠政治魄力<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-27<br />\n <br />\n本身是律師的民主黨立法會議員涂謹申認為，一旦政府引入《緊急法》，禁止市民集會示威，就等同宣布戒嚴，只會令「和理非」市民都同政府強烈對立，反效果非常大。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申不認為引入《緊急法》，社會就能回復平靜，而是缺乏政治魄力的做法，而且在現時中美貿易戰升級的形勢下，只會為中央政府添煩添亂。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，記憶中《緊急法》在「六七暴動」時，港英政府曾經引用過，當年是用來鎮壓左派動亂，認為無助解決現時的社會局勢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477051-20190827.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477051-20190827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=932c9074\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477051-20190827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cf49a33b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477051-20190827.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"daf79c448081ea50586c5c76016ab3e4c28bf4ad","tid":1510030,"uid":14094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"搶"},{"pid":"3d726d03104950e37a4d59da30bc60e4ba393d74","tid":1510030,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左今天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2c10b0769eda50e70222c1dba69357fe23b5eb89","